summary: An ordinance providing for the acquisition for general municipal purposes of certain tax title property in Blocks 63 and 64, Replat of West Seattle Land and Improvement Company's Third Plat, Block 11, Beacon Hill View and Block 71, West Seattle Third Plat, for the payment of delinquent taxes and local improvement assessments thereon and to discharge the trust; making a reimbursable appropriation from the Emergency Fund and declaring the emergency therefor.
committee: Finance and Parks and Public Grounds
